{"tid":988701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【被困六天】2歲西班牙囝囝跌落油井鑽孔 救援人員鑽新隧道希望救到","createTime":"2019-01-20T09:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T22:15:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"d961eae18747029c3244261c985b43ca0e416182","tid":988701,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"西班牙一名2歲幼童誤墮110米深的油井鑽孔，被困已經一周，拯救工程困難，因男童誤墮的鑽孔孔洞狹窄，團隊無法從該處使用挖掘機器拯救他，專家研究鑽掘一條水平通道，希望在36小時內盡快拯救到他。<br />\n事發在馬拉加（Malaga），地點是2歲男童尤倫（Julen）的家族屬地，其父親事發當天親眼看着兒子跌入井，他憶述︰「我燒幾根柴後，跑向他&hellip;&hellip;我的表親比較近一點，當我跑向井時，她整個人都撲倒地上&hellip;&hellip;尤倫已經消失了，我一開始聽到他哭，但一會兒已經再也聽不到了。」<br />\n傷心欲絕的他又指︰「我太太當時要去打個電話，說不去上班，她原本與尤倫在一起，打電話時，叫我看着尤倫，她只有幾呎遠&hellip;&hellip;我去撿幾根柴，準備煮飯，而尤倫就開始跑了。」這對夫婦原本還有一個3歲長子，但他在2年前因先天心臟問題逝世，幼子尤倫是他們現在唯一的兒子。有家族成員指，該口井是早前為了尋找水源而挖掘，並有依法例蓋好洞口，不過尤倫的家人指涉事者只在洞穴上鋪了數塊石頭，沒有將之妥善覆蓋。<br />\n據報指為了營救尤倫，當局使用了最好的鑽挖機器，又有專家從北部地區趕到研究鑽挖方法。預計鑽挖新通道工程要花15小時。由於營救工作分秒必爭，團隊未能如普通工程般先做好測量工作，預計鑽挖時如遇大石更會阻礙工程。但成功後，將會放置可載兩人的氧氣囊入去，將尤倫帶回地面。<br />\n被困多日的尤倫依靠一個提供食水的氧氣包維生，警方及私人公司的專家表示，相信尤倫仍然有機會生存。事件引起公眾關注，社交網站發起標籤「MimanoaJulen」（支持尤倫），為他打氣。救援人員未能跟尤倫說到話，但他父親表示「不會放棄，仍期望他生還」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547952166_a4f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547952166_a4f2.jpg&h=31112317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547952172_0a14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547952172_0a14.jpg&h=5af6c227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547952166_d4f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547952166_d4f5.jpg&h=4a83864c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547952166_a336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547952166_a336.jpg&h=6f4232ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59163085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163085&d=DiHeWtdYrRpCJzMVDAV9vgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e84e6386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59163085&h=d3196885\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59163085</a>"},{"pid":"e08b72cafe2ea60e153559dab4db87b0f01fe785","tid":988701,"uid":13303,"like":156,"dislike":8,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子呀.jpg<br />\n個井會彈返個仔出黎"},{"pid":"cbf335d30f0150672192a9ba60f84b021838a89a","tid":988701,"uid":168730,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:52:01.000Z","msg":"110米=30幾層樓高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ea93c0a6cc109b03b8329d010a806b186c57b0","tid":988701,"uid":26451,"like":144,"dislike":13,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3d8ca64cff4ce2ebbb7d28649bdb70f41788e52","tid":988701,"uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":37,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"Elon Musk 仲唔出黎鳩up 點救個細路出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef67f4a52d59fec82a21de5629a22204717d22b","tid":988701,"uid":2676,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:57:28.000Z","msg":"2歲死撚緊啦"},{"pid":"8d9414455765c2f98aa38629dc21eecf88bfc7a8","tid":988701,"uid":46849,"like":62,"dislike":7,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"好地地帶個 2 歲既去荒山野嶺做乜鳩"},{"pid"